# SimpleOS Font Directory
#
# Open-source fonts for 10 languages across 6 script groups.
# All fonts are OFL-1.1 (SIL Open Font License) — free for any use.
#
# Run download_fonts.shs to fetch all fonts from GitHub releases.
#
# Font Organization:
#   fonts/
#     sans/           — Sans-serif (UI default)
#     serif/          — Serif (document reading)
#     mono/           — Monospace (code, terminal)
#
# Script Coverage:
#
# | Script Group       | Languages                          | Sans Font              | Serif Font              | Mono Font       |
# |--------------------|------------------------------------|------------------------|-------------------------|-----------------|
# | Latin + Cyrillic   | English, Spanish, French,          | Noto Sans              | Noto Serif              | Fira Code Nerd* |
# |                    | Portuguese, Russian                |                        |                         |  (default mono) |
# | CJK (Simplified)   | Chinese (Mandarin)                 | Noto Sans SC           | Noto Serif SC           | (use Sans)      |
# | Hangul             | Korean                             | Noto Sans KR           | Noto Serif KR           | D2Coding        |
# | Devanagari         | Hindi                              | Noto Sans Devanagari*  | Noto Serif Devanagari*  | (use Sans)      |
# | Arabic             | Arabic                             | Noto Sans Arabic*      | Noto Naskh Arabic*      | (use Sans)      |
# | Bengali            | Bengali                            | Noto Sans Bengali*     | Noto Serif Bengali*     | (use Sans)      |
#
# * = Requires HarfBuzz for complex text shaping (future Tier 2)
#
# Tier 1 (stb_truetype): Latin, Cyrillic, CJK, Korean — simple glyph lookup
# Tier 2 (HarfBuzz):     Hindi, Arabic, Bengali — complex shaping + RTL
#
# * Fira Code Nerd Font Mono is the SimpleOS default monospace face. It
#   bundles Nerd Font glyphs (powerline separators, devicons, git/folder/
#   lock icons) required by the shell Starship-style prompt. The well-known
#   path `SYSTEM_DEFAULT_MONO_FONT_PATH` lives in
#   src/lib/common/text_layout/font_renderer.spl.
#   JetBrains Mono is kept as a fallback (no Nerd glyphs).
#
# Approximate sizes:
#   Sans only (1 weight): ~22 MB full / ~5.7 MB subsetted
#   All types (1 weight): ~50 MB full / ~12 MB subsetted
